# USB Drive Whitelist for flash-to-usb.sh
#
# Entry formats:
#   1. Serial match — put the drive's exact serial on a line by itself.
#   2. Vendor/Model match — `model:VENDOR/MODEL [max=NG] [min=NG]`
#      Matches ANY drive with that vendor+model within the size range.
#      Use this to whitelist a whole product line (e.g. buy a pack of 10).
#
# Run './build-scripts/flash-to-usb.sh --list' to see connected drives.
# Only drives matching an entry here will be offered as targets.
#
# Examples:
# ABC123456789
# model:Verbatim/STORE N GO max=20G
